<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>2FA Disabled</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f59e0b 0%, #d97706 100%); color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
        .warning { background: #fef3c7; border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b; padding: 12px; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>⚠️ Two-Factor Authentication Disabled</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
        
        <div class="warning">
            <strong>⚠️ Security Notice:</strong> Two-factor authentication has been disabled on your {{appName}} account.
        </div>

        <p>Your account now has reduced security. We strongly recommend re-enabling 2FA to protect your account.</p>

        <p><strong>Time:</strong> 2FA was disabled at {{disabledAt}}</p>

        <p>If you didn't disable 2FA on your account, please:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Change your password immediately</li>
            <li>Re-enable 2FA</li>
            <li>Contact support if you need assistance</li>
        </ol>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>© 2025 {{appName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

